title: 704. Dark-horse Super Bowl Contenders
itunes:title: 704. Dark-horse Super Bowl Contenders
description:
Bucky Brooks is back with a new episode of Move the Sticks with special guest Lance Zierlein. On this show, the guys start by reacting to the first episode of Hard Knocks featuring the Dallas Cowboys. Following that, the duo talk about the situation surrounding Texans quarterback Deshaun Watson in Houston. To wrap up the show, Bucky and Lance each give dark-horse Super Bowl contenders.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
